{"word":"G5191 - ὑακίνθινος - hyakínthinos - hoo-ak-in'-thee-nos - Jacinth","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑακίνθινος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyakínthinos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoo-ak-in'-thee-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Jacinth</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நீலநிறமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of hyacinth, of the color of hyacinth"},{"paragraph":"\"கரும்சிவப்பு\""},{"paragraph":"\"darkred\""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5192 - ὑάκινθος - hyákinthos - hoo-ak'-in-thos/5192\">G5192</a>; &ldquo;hyacinthine&rdquo; or &ldquo;jacinthine&rdquo;, that is, deep <i>blue:</i> - jacinth.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}